{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775863596459,"sessionID":"ses_286483c20ffeCB3c9r8P9Xxksn","part":{"id":"prt_d79b80219001tHbzULPFgCS5WL","messageID":"msg_d79b7f5be001AtdcKc2B4zz3aT","sessionID":"ses_286483c20ffeCB3c9r8P9Xxksn","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_55bb852c59ed4037a59009c5","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-022/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-022/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-022 — CLI publish 命令 Tasks\n2: \n3: **Module:** cmd/cli  \n4: **Language:** Python  \n5: **Size:** L  \n6: **Stage:** ST-3 (Design Completed)\n7: \n8: ---\n9: \n10: ## Phase 1: Prerequisites Validation\n11: \n12: - [ ] **T101** Implement `_validate_publish_prerequisites(workspace_path)` in `PublishRuntime`\n13:   - *Verify:* Raises `FileNotFoundError` when workspace path does not exist\n14:   - *Verify:* Raises `FileNotFoundError` when `agent_metadata.yaml` missing\n15: \n16: - [ ] **T102** Validate AgentCube provider prerequisites\n17:   - *Verify:* Raises `ValueError` when `provider=\"agentcube\"` and `router_url` missing\n18:   - *Verify:* Raises `ValueError` when `provider=\"agentcube\"` and `workload_manager_url` missing\n19: \n20: ---\n21: \n22: ## Phase 2: Image Preparation\n23: \n24: - [ ] **T201** Implement `_prepare_local_image(workspace_path, metadata)` method\n25:   - *Verify:* Uses locally built image from metadata when `build_mode=\"local\"`\n26: \n27: - [ ] **T202** Implement `_prepare_cloud_image(workspace_path, metadata)` method  \n28:   - *Verify:* Uses cloud registry image URL when `build_mode=\"cloud\"`\n29: \n30: - [ ] **T203** Implement image push to registry in `_prepare_image_for_publishing`\n31:   - *Verify:* Pushes image when `image_username` and `image_password` provided\n32:   - *Verify:* Returns pushed image URL after successful push\n33: \n34: ---\n35: \n36: ## Phase 3: AgentCube Provider Deployment\n37: \n38: - [ ] **T301** Enhance `AgentCubeProvider.deploy_agent_runtime()` to include CR environment variables\n39:   - *Verify:* Embeds `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL` from metadata\n40:   - *Verify:* Embeds `ROUTER_URL` from metadata\n41:   - *Verify:* Sets `sessionTimeout` to `\"15m\"`\n42:   - *Verify:* Sets `maxSessionDuration` to `\"8h\"`\n43:   - *Verify:* References `imagePullSecrets` as `[{\"name\": \"default-secret\"}]`\n44: \n45: - [ ] **T302** Update metadata with AgentRuntime deployment info\n46:   - *Verify:* Saves `agent_id` to metadata after successful deployment\n47: \n48: ---\n49: \n50: ## Phase 4: Kubernetes Provider Deployment\n51: \n52: - [ ] **T401** Implement `wait_for_deployment_ready(namespace, deployment_name, timeout=120)` in `KubernetesProvider`\n53:   - *Verify:* Waits up to 120 seconds for pods to be ready\n54:   - *Verify:* Raises `TimeoutError` if timeout exceeded\n55: \n56: - [ ] **T402** Update K8s deployment metadata\n57:   - *Verify:* Saves `k8s_deployment` with: `deployment_name`, `service_name`, `namespace`, `replicas`, `container_port`, `node_port`, `service_url`\n58: \n59: ---\n60: \n61: ## Phase 5: Version Handling\n62: \n63: - [ ] **T501** Implement version handling logic in `PublishRuntime.publish()`\n64:   - *Verify:* Uses `--version` from CLI if provided\n65:   - *Verify:* Falls back to `metadata.version` if CLI version not provided\n66:   - *Verify:* Defaults to `\"latest\"` if no version in CLI or metadata\n67: \n68: ---\n69: \n70: ## Phase 6: Error Handling\n71: \n72: - [ ] **T601** Enhance error messages with verbose logging\n73:   - *Verify:* Prints full traceback when `--verbose` enabled\n74:   - *Verify:* Prints error only (no traceback) when `--verbose` disabled\n75: \n76: - [ ] **T602** Handle K8s readiness timeout error\n77:   - *Verify:* Records error in metadata when timeout occurs\n78: \n79: ---\n80: \n81: ## Phase 7: Success Output\n82: \n83: - [ ] **T701** Enhance success output with complete deployment details\n84:   - *Verify:* Displays: Agent name, Provider type (agentcube/k8s), Deployment namespace\n85:   - *Verify:* Displays: Service URL for K8s or AgentRuntime info for AgentCube\n86: \n87: ---\n88: \n89: ## Phase 8: Testing\n90: \n91: - [ ] **T801** Write unit tests for `_validate_publish_prerequisites`\n92:   - *Verify:* `pytest tests/test_publish_runtime.py -v -k \"test_validate\"`\n93: \n94: - [ ] **T802** Write unit tests for version handling\n95:   - *Verify:* Tests CLI version, metadata version, and default \"latest\"\n96: \n97: - [ ] **T803** Write unit tests for `_prepare_image_for_publishing`\n98:   - *Verify:* Tests local mode, cloud mode, and registry push\n99: \n100: - [ ] **T804** Write unit tests for `wait_for_deployment_ready`\n101:   - *Verify:* Tests timeout behavior\n102: \n103: ---\n104: \n105: ## Verification Commands\n106: \n107: ```bash\n108: # CLI help\n109: kubectl-agentcube publish --help\n110: \n111: # Publish to AgentCube (default)\n112: kubectl-agentcube publish -f /path/to/workspace\n113: \n114: # Publish to K8s\n115: kubectl-agentcube publish -f /path/to/workspace --provider k8s\n116: \n117: # Publish with custom version\n118: kubectl-agentcube publish -f . --version v1.0.0\n119: \n120: # Publish with K8s options\n121: kubectl-agentcube publish -f . --provider k8s --node-port 30001 --replicas 2\n122: \n123: # Run publish tests\n124: pytest tests/test_publish_runtime.py -v\n125: \n126: # Run lint\n127: ruff check agentcube/\n128: ruff format agentcube/\n129: \n130: # Run typecheck\n131: mypy agentcube/\n132: ```\n133: \n134: ---\n135: \n136: ## Dependencies\n137: \n138: - Requires: AR-021 (build command) completed\n139: - Uses: `agentcube/services/agentcube_provider.py`\n140: - Uses: `agentcube/services/k8s_provider.py`\n141: - Uses: `agentcube/services/docker_service.py`\n142: - Uses: `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py`\n143: - Uses: `agentcube/runtime/build_runtime.py` (pattern reference)\n144: \n145: ---\n146: \n147: ## Acceptance Criteria (from delta-spec)\n148: \n149: - [ ] AC001: Publish command accepts all specified CLI options\n150: - [ ] AC002: Publish validates workspace and metadata exist before proceeding\n151: - [ ] AC003: Publish validates AgentCube prerequisites (router_url, workload_manager_url)\n152: - [ ] AC004: Publish prepares image for registry (local or cloud mode)\n153: - [ ] AC005: Publish deploys AgentRuntime CR when provider is \"agentcube\"\n154: - [ ] AC006: Publish deploys K8s Deployment/Service when provider is \"k8s\"\n155: - [ ] AC007: Publish waits for K8s deployment readiness (timeout: 120s)\n156: - [ ] AC008: Publish handles version from CLI, metadata, or default \"latest\"\n157: - [ ] AC009: Publish updates metadata with deployment information\n158: - [ ] AC010: Publish displays success output with Rich formatting\n159: - [ ] AC011: Publish handles errors with appropriate exit codes and verbose logging\n160: \n161: ---\n162: \n163: ## Notes\n164: \n165: - Design stage ST-3 complete - implementation ready\n166: - Publish supports two providers: \"agentcube\" (AgentRuntime CR) and \"k8s\" (Deployment + NodePort Service)\n167: - Image push to registry requires `--image-username` and `--image-password`\n168: - K8s deployment waits up to 120 seconds for pods to become ready\n\n(End of file - total 168 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-022 — CLI publish 命令 Tasks\n\n**Module:** cmd/cli  \n**Language:** Python  \n**Size:** L  \n**Stage:** ST-3 (Design Completed)\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1: Prerequisites Validation\n\n- [ ] **T101** Implement `_validate_publish_prerequisites(workspace_path)` in `PublishRuntime`\n  - *Verify:* Raises `FileNotFoundError` when workspace path does not exist\n  - *Verify:* Raises `FileNotFoundError` when `agent_metadata.yaml` missing\n\n- [ ] **T102** Validate AgentCube provider prerequisites\n  - *Verify:* Raises `ValueError` when `provider=\"agentcube\"` and `router_url` missing\n  - *Verify:* Raises `ValueError` when `provider=\"agentcube\"` and `workload_manager_url` missing\n\n---","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-022/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775863596425,"end":1775863596457}}}}
